nodes.text: The Duinarbulon Archives was a archive on the planet Duinarbulon. According to records held in the archive, prior to the Devouring—a campaign of extermination by the Hutts in 24,500 BBY against the Tionese colonies of the Kiirium Reaches—the Hutts had raided the planets of the Kiirium Reaches for slaves for centuries but left the worlds largely unharmed.
